0.1.name: wordpress/interactive-maps
0.1.description: Includes an HTML5, JavaScript-powered map of the world with hoverable continents and location markers. This map can be downloaded and customized easily using a text editor. Upon customization, the map can be easily uploaded to WordPress and inserted into a post or page using this plugin.
